title: Atelier.Ayesha.The.Alchemist.of.Dusk.PS3-DUPLEX
description: Atelier Ayesha: The Alchemist of Dusk is a Japanese role-playing video game developed by Gust. The character designs are by Hidari. It is the fourteenth title in the Atelier after Atelier Meruru, but has a storyline independent from previous titles in the series. A March 2013 release is being distributed by Tecmo Koei in western regions, with NIS America doing the translation work.
